description.value: On a critical hit, the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.VcDeM8A5oI6VqhbM]{Restrained} instead. The Bone Prancer may only restrain one creature in this manner.
On a critical hit, the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.VcDeM8A5oI6VqhbM]{Restrained} instead. The Bone Prancer may only restrain one creature in this manner.
If the Bone Prancer moved over 10 feet before attacking, it deals an additional [[/r 2d8 #damage]]{2d8 damage}.

The prancer is incapacitated while in the area of an @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.My7FvAoLYgGDDBzy]{Antimagic Field}. If targeted by the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.9HpwDN4MYQJnW0LG]{Dispel Magic} spell, the prancer must succeed on a @Check[fortitude] saving throw against the caster's spell save DC or fall @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious} for 1 minute.
On a critical hit, the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.VcDeM8A5oI6VqhbM]{Restrained} instead. The Bone Prancer may only restrain one creature in this manner.

The Bone Prancer may stride up to its Speed. If it has a creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.VcDeM8A5oI6VqhbM]{Restrained}, it may move them with itself. The restrained creatures suffers @Damage[2d6[bludgeoning]] damage for every 10 feet moved in this manner.
